title: Muir Woods National Monument: Places To Go
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Places To Go             Places To Go         Muir Woods is part of the Golden Gate National Recreation Area (GGNRA). GGNRA offers a diverse range of natural and cultural sites to explore, extending across San Mateo, San Francisco, and Marin counties. To learn more about the following locations, please visit GGNRA.
